                             @{U}@{B}Words about this Guide@{UU}@{UB}

This guide is an informationsystem. You find information about the latest known
versions and the authors of the classes. You also find, if I know, important or
additional informations to the classes. But you find nothing about contents, use
or installing of them. @{B}See also the MUI and MCC documents!@{UB}

@{"MUI" link MUI} is shareware, most of the MCC-Lib's are freeware, but not all of them! You
should lock in the documents for copyright's and freeware, shareware or other
informations about use and permissions. This guide will only give a overview
about newest and/or existing versions.

