@NODE "MUI40FAKE" "Fakes, Trojans and other warnings"
@TOC Main
@NEXT Authors
@PREV UPDATE



@{JCENTER}@{U}@{B}MUI 4.0 - a fake and more@{UU}@{UB}
@{JLEFT}
  After I heared from it, I searched for it, and found it. The @{B}MUI40USR.lha@{UB}
  exists. But it is no new version, it is a faked @{B}MUI38USR.lha@{UB} witj lots
  of changes. If you look inside this chapter because you search informations,
  then reat it. If VersCheck show you a warning that it one ore more parts of
  your system found, jump to the end of this text, you find all faked files!


  @{U}@{I}Changes between the real MUI3.8 and the faked MUI4.0:@{UU}@{UI}
  
  This all aare patches, replacement with trojan or anything in this case.

   * Deleting all below listed MUI programs, library's, from list below.

   * install MUI from a secret place (CP, SASG homepage, AmiNet (server/cd)
     again.

   * testing system by a anti virus tool! Ny test show that VT is the only
     program that find the faket MUI, but only 3 from 15)


  @{U}@{I}What do the faake doing:@{UU}@{UI}

  This text says whaat I believe and think, afer analyse the files aand read
  the fact from VT's warning.

   * From changed Install-MUI a program is startet, that will replace a Shell
     script in the MUI goodies dir. No anti-virus programmer, crypter or
     anything else has seen it decryptet. It is a secret, what goes on if it
     start.

   * Two things, that simple to find (and shure not the kern functions):

   @{B}--- Why it isn't an apriljoke ---@{UB}

       The package has the date 01-APRIL-1999. It SEEM to be a april joke
     . Messages in MUI und PSI say it also. But, there are files that are
       dated to 02-april-99 Nobody make such a big april joke and comes one
       day to late.@{U}@{I}This is BULLSHIT!@{UU}@{UI}

   @{B}--- What do it really??? -------@{UB}

       The patches includen a part, that give a hint. All seem to be a email
       function, sending a email to Stefan Stunz with more than unfine content.
       I think, this part is real, but not 100 % correct.

       But when this mails really be send, mail will never reach SASG. If
       anyone has a closed network, he can check it out. I think, the mail go
       not to SASG. The mail go to the autor invisible packed in  the big
       shot part..
       And the mail brings more as the visible text. Possible for such a
       subpack is aany file. Perhapy it get your passwords und accounts (if
       yo, the pack is 100 % to for BBS systems.

       Or, the will be searching for licence files, config, keyfiles, and
       yo on. I have no change to start such a software, because it can be
       dangerous for the security of my software and harddisks. If I hear
       more, it will pot also in my guide.

   * Likely, if you have the software running and all things woring. Why not,
     it is really MUI 3.8, copied and with a little add ons.

   * I don't know what happens if a part of the software is running or startet
     and date is first april anyyear.

     @{B}############################################################@{UB}
     @{B}###@{I}@{UB} what's real, what's faked, how find the faked files? @{UI}@{B}###@{UB}
     @{B}############################################################@{UB}


