@{B}WANTED: MUI-Author@{UB}

I created this Guide, because the informations are not included in the existing Guide in the moment and the work on them are much enough work for the authors.

But, I programming without use of MUI and I think the programmers of the MUI classes have most the newest and best informations, better than my.

So I think this work can better done by any of this people. If you programming with MUI and want to do this work in future, please contact me to do so.

For the time no insider do so, I do the work.
  
